_note: seed pairs recorded during the audit - each round is one rotation

rounds.note: first round - autobet, extension v1.4 didnt capture per-bet nonces. verified retroactively after adding low prob table to verifier - nonces 1-100 sequential, all match.

rounds.nonces_confirmed: via winna history tab - nonces 1-30 sequential
rounds.note: full verification complete. algorithm confirmed: HMAC-SHA256 byte generator with cumulative probability distribution. nonces start at 1.
second full verification. different difficulty (high) from round 2 (medium). played manually to keep nonce order. confirms algorithm works across difficulties.

algorithm.type: HMAC-SHA256 byte generator + cumulative probability distribution
algorithm.byte_generator: HMAC-SHA256(serverSeed, clientSeed:nonce:cursor) - yields 32 bytes per hash, cursor increments
algorithm.outcome_determination: single float mapped against cumulative probability distribution table (NOT individual pin decisions)
algorithm.note: this is NOT the common L/R per-pin approach. winna uses weighted probability distribution per bucket.

findings.house_edge_note: displayed multipliers have house edge applied (0.49x instead of 0.5x, 0.99x instead of 1x)
findings.zero_bets_note: $0 bets (even with logged in account) do not increment the nonce. server-side nonce tracking ignores zero-amount plays.
